 exchange across the wing membranes represents 5%\u201310% of the total in E. wahlbergi.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Minnaar, Ingrid A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bennett, Nigel C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chimimba, Christian T.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "McKechnie, Andrew E.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/0639ffd4c0db15efabb64598ce41327a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/0fdda999208c50f4de0517a9a380d72708d04f5fd5069ad170d539c6465eeca3", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/LERXWMWT", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/LERXWMWT", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/716549586f2d660b338acbee65d17303!/b88987-91453", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/26f7ce5dd404e33c6570edd4ba250d20", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "475-485", "title": "Physiological and Biochemical Zoology", "volume": "87"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/0639ffd4c0db15efabb64598ce41327a"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:LERXWMWT"}, {"identifier": "10.1086/675342"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13440904"